    "curator_notes": "The Kikaninchen Hörspiel series 'Mein Geschichtenkissen!' contains gentle bedtime stories for young children featuring the KiKA mascot. Albums 01 and 02 are the core Hörspiel releases with 10 stories each. The artist page contains many music compilation albums (Kinderlieder, Party Mixes) which are curated as separate music content, not Hörspiele. Kikaninchen has been a popular KiKA (Kinderkanal) character since 2008 as cross-media content. Interestingly, this Spotify artist page mixes original Kikaninchen music content with generic 'Karussell' branded compilation albums that are not specifically Kikaninchen content - they are divided by theme rather than character. The two episodes provide approx. 19 short stories total."
